urred on Rakhat. The Sparrow was about a man's spiritual journey, and that was lost in the sequel's massive focus on the VaRakhati war.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eFinally, it was just really unnecessary. The Sparrow was emotionally brutal and that's part of what made it so impressive. This sequel neuters that brutality, and while it's nice seeing Emilio having some happy moments, The Sparrow made sense as it was - it told a story in a way that it needed to be told. ","rating":2,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/126262?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"science-fiction","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/126262?shelf=science-fiction"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"2009","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/126262?shelf=2009"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/45325201"},"likeCount":66,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":10,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:56035852":{"id":56035852,"__typename":"User","legacyId":56035852,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1469958232i/56035852._UY200_CR50,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":229,"viewableName":"Katie","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/56035852-katie","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":298},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.rjhTBD-EWVX2apcFT-Uv8g":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.rjhTBD-EWVX2apcFT-Uv8g","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.c_AS6V134Z5CMzAhupeUwA"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:56035852"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1639561116004,"createdAt":1561375243955,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1561543945890,"text":"I loved The Sparrow and 